place.name: EATON
place.gazetteerText: EATON-ST. ANDREW, a parish in Norwich district, Norfolk; within Norwich city. Real property, £8, 759. Pop., 930. Houses, 191. The living is a vicarage in the diocese of Norwich. Value, £87. Patrons, the Dean and Chapter of Norwich. (In 1870-72, John Marius Wilson's Imperial Gazetteer of England and Wales)
